Subject: [PATCH] Cat73 -> Do not load chunks for light checks
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

不要在亮度检测时加载区块
这种区块加载只会出现在最边缘的区块依赖周围未加载区块的光照源时，其实并没有神马意义
而且区块加载后检测完亮度马上就会被作为无效区块被卸载，很浪费资源
Link: https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/blob/468a1cbbd78384f2c728ef93d5f796d8b9891a7e/Spigot-Server-Patches/0090-Do-not-load-chunks-for-light-checks.patch

diff --git a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/World.java b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/World.java
index 45f27974..14350594 100644
--- a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/World.java
+++ b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/World.java
@@ -650,6 +650,7 @@ public abstract class World implements IEntityAccess, GeneratorAccess, IIBlockAc
                 if (blockposition.getY() >= 256) {
                     blockposition = new BlockPosition(blockposition.getX(), 255, blockposition.getZ());
                 }
+                if (!this.isLoaded(blockposition)) return 0; // Paper
 
                 return this.getChunkAtWorldCoords(blockposition).a(blockposition, i);
             }
